Program: Outlook
Title: Inside the Mind of a Forensic Pathologist
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswl5n
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 19 Oct 2018
Dr Richard Shepherd has worked on some of Britain's most high profile crime scenes including the site of the death of Diana, Princess of Wales. Bernie Dalton always wanted to record an album of his songs but when he lost his voice as a result of motor neurone disease, singer Essence Goldman stepped in. Outlook's Jason Reinier went to meet her. (Image: Dr Richard Shepherd. Credit: BBC) Show less